# 🔍 Reconnaissance

The SSH service was identified using Nmap.

### Command used

```bash
nmap -sV -p 2222 localhost
```

### Result

| Port     | State | Service | Version      |
| -------- | ----- | ------- | ------------ |
| 2222/tcp | open  | ssh     | OpenSSH 10.2 |

The scan confirmed that the SSH service was reachable and exposed on port 2222.

